{"tid":1125753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內蒙古化工廠凌晨爆炸    火光照亮黑夜 3死5傷","createTime":"2019-04-26T02:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T05:08:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc0dc315b55be5bb25bb6fe874b0979b341332f","tid":1125753,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"內蒙古東興化工有限責任公司24日凌晨2時55分左右發生爆燃，已造成3死5傷，據了解，事發公司烏蘭察布市卓資縣內最大的工業項目，年產40萬噸聚氯乙烯、32萬噸燒鹼、60萬噸電石及100萬噸水泥，傷者已經送往附近的醫院進行救治，而事發原因目前還在調查當中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4047/4047750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4047%2F4047750.jpg&h=9268950d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《新京報》指出，當地緊急疏散周圍人員，周邊區域部分民房受損。附近居民講，爆燃發生後，廠里工作的親屬跑出來逐戶通知讓撤離，周邊停放的車玻璃被衝擊波擊碎。<br />\n<br />\n在曝光的畫面中，可以看到暗黑的夜空中閃現大量的火光，四周建築的窗戶受到爆炸波的衝擊，都出現明顯受損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190424/1429662.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190424%2F1429662.htm&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=f24cbf48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190424/1429662.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e991faa8850ec986e15576494c36b1d9f40dba71","tid":1125753,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"支爆"},{"pid":"e7dba1ff05d1d00f4bdd607169107d01627ed98a","tid":1125753,"uid":91631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"接二連三咁爆<br />\n<br />\n似係人為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e20995a0b04923d13a36941df0609805fb18c","tid":1125753,"uid":130695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔俾你執笠 咁炸撚左佢"},{"pid":"dd051df77cc4608eee5b90bbe6317b823a0db1ad","tid":1125753,"uid":50386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:18:57.000Z","msg":"隨時伊拉克都冇支那爆得咁密<im